OL,3,CSurge of domestic abuse calls received
OL,4,Cby PSNI peaked on New Year's Day
OL,6,FThe annual surge in domestic abuse
OL,7,Fcalls received by police in Northern
OL,8,FIreland over Christmas peaked on New
OL,9,FYear's Day, figures have indicated.
OL,11,FThere were an average of 92 calls a
OL,12,Fday to police between December 20 and
OL,13,FJanuary 2 2025.
OL,15,FThe highest number (127) was received
OL,16,Fon January 1, followed by 109 on
OL,17,FDecember 27 and 102 on Boxing Day.
