OL,3,CSurge of domestic abuse calls received
OL,4,Cby PSNI peaked on New Year's Day
OL,6,FIn total, there were 1,288 domestic
OL,7,Fabuse calls to police between December
OL,8,F20 and January 2, a fall from 1,336 in
OL,9,Fthe same period during 2023/24.
OL,11,FPSNI figures also indicate that the
OL,12,Fnumber of calls received was lower on
OL,13,Fmost days when compared with the
OL,14,Fprevious two time periods during 2022-
OL,15,F2023 and 2023-2024.
OL,17,FThe daily average number of calls (92)
OL,18,Fwas lower than for the five years 2020
OL,19,Fto 2024 combined (98) and the five
OL,20,Fyears 2015 to 2019 combined (98).
