OL,3,CSurge of domestic abuse calls received
OL,4,Cby PSNI peaked on New Year's Day
OL,6,FHoweve,r the daily average number of
OL,7,Fcalls was higher than the daily
OL,8,Faverage across both the month of
OL,9,FDecember (84) and across the whole
OL,10,Fyear (80), in a similar pattern that
OL,11,Fhas been seen over the last 10 years.
OL,13,FCommissioner designate for victims of
OL,14,Fcrime Geraldine Hanna expressed
OL,15,Fsadness at the numbers.
OL,17,F"It is truly tragic that there was, on
OL,18,Faverage, 92 domestic abuse calls a day
OL,19,Fto the police over the Christmas
OL,20,Fperiod," she said.
