OL,6,F"Victims of domestic abuse often talk
OL,7,Fabout how the festive period is a time
OL,8,Fof particular danger for them and this
OL,9,Fis sadly reflected in this data.
OL,11,F"Over the last number of years, we
OL,12,Fhave increasingly heard the message
OL,13,Ffrom government and the criminal
OL,14,Fjustice system that domestic abuse is
OL,15,Funacceptable and victims should come
OL,16,Fforward.
