OL,6,F"The challenge now for them is to make
OL,7,Fsure their actions match those
OL,8,Fmessages. Victims need properly
OL,9,Fresourced support and a criminal
OL,10,Fjustice system that deals with their
OL,11,Fcases efficiently and in a trauma-
OL,12,Finformed way.
OL,14,F"I am pleased to see the police
OL,15,Fpublishing this data. Capturing data
OL,16,Flike this is a key step in
OL,17,Funderstanding and combatting domestic
OL,18,Fabuse. Publishing it helps to inform
OL,19,Fthe public and provide transparency.
